{"tid":1898463,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[hunter]其實希索卡根本係忠角黎","createTime":"2020-02-26T05:55:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T09:03:21.000Z","uid":51411,"like":77,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":58,"replies":[{"pid":"2fbcb69e03d879abdc240350b6b8b5269da12eaf","tid":1898463,"uid":51411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"明明大奸角既形象但成套漫畫佢最好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最初獵人考試如果冇佢讓賽 <br />\n主角三人組（除咗基路亞）根本過唔到關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後到天空鬥技場200樓唔比小剛同基路亞入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話佢地未夠班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後坐咗成晚走廊等佢地變強返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後拍賣會篇又比情報古拿比加<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nGreen island篇唔洗講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拿尼加篇又特登激尻伊耳謎搞到佢比基路亞發現<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一次睇都唔覺 <br />\n第二次睇開始覺得唔係好合理<br />\n而家已經當佢係忠角算<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5903d3e916ca41df5ad5bdbcdeb0e899937b6a64","tid":1898463,"uid":247184,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"quote":{"pid":"2fbcb69e03d879abdc240350b6b8b5269da12eaf","tid":1898463,"uid":51411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-26T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"明明大奸角既形象但成套漫畫佢最好人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最初獵人考試如果冇佢讓賽 <br />\n主角三人組（除咗基路亞）根本過唔到關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後到天空鬥技場200樓唔比小剛同基路亞入<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話佢地未夠班<img src=\"/as